#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 17. Pāpabhikkhusutta → bhikkhusuttaṃ (bj) | bhikkhu (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Pāpabhikkhusutta "
msgstr "17. A Bad Monk "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.261, sc1
msgctxt "sn19.17:1.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ bhikkhuṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. "
msgstr "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a monk flying through the air. "

#. VAR: sajotibhūtā → sañjotibhūtā (s1-3, km) | sajotibhūto (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.17:1.2"
msgid "Tassa saṅghāṭipi ādittā sampajjalitā sajotibhūtā, pattopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto, kāyabandhanampi ādittaṃ sampajjalitaṃ sajotibhūtaṃ, kāyopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto. "
msgstr "His outer robe, bowl, belt, and body were burning, blazing, and glowing "

msgctxt "sn19.17:1.3"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … "
msgstr "as he screamed in pain. …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.17:1.4"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kassapassa sammāsambuddhassa pāvacane pāpabhikkhu ahosi … pe …. "
msgstr "“That monk used to be a bad monk in the time of Buddha Kassapa’s dispensation. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.17:1.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

